OL,3,CDriving instructor 'still trying to
OL,4,Cfunction' after ex-pupil stalked him
OL,6,FA driving instructor who was stalked
OL,7,Fby an ex-pupil says officers need to
OL,8,Fbe "educated" on the long-lasting
OL,9,Fimpact of the crime following a
OL,10,Fscathing report into police failings.
OL,12,FBob Coughtrey, 60, from the Flyde
OL,13,FCoast, says he is still "trying to
OL,14,Ffunction" and is "always on his guard"
OL,15,Fafter he was stalked by a student
OL,16,Fafter she passed her test in 2017.
OL,18,FShe sent weeks of text messages,
OL,19,Fincluding the words "hurt" and "stab",
OL,20,Fand later turned up at his home and
OL,21,Fthreatened to kill him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
