OL,3,CDriving instructor 'still trying to
OL,4,Cfunction' after ex-pupil stalked him
OL,6,FThree official watchdogs have found
OL,7,Fstalking victims are being "let down."
OL,8,FIn too many cases, police "failed to
OL,9,Frecognise stalking or take the
OL,10,Fnecessary steps to protect victims."
OL,12,FBob said he thought the report was
OL,13,F"absolutely spot on" and revealed a
OL,14,Fview of "almost indifference" to
OL,15,Fstalking by the authorities and
OL,16,Fsociety as a whole.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
