OL,3,CDriving instructor 'still trying to
OL,4,Cfunction' after ex-pupil stalked him
OL,6,FHe said: "They're seeing it as a just
OL,7,Fa bit of interest - someone's giving
OL,8,Fyou a bit of attention. It's not
OL,9,Fattention, it's not interest, and it's
OL,10,Fcertainly not invited or wanted.
OL,12,F"Police officers are still a member of
OL,13,Fsociety, let's face it. I know a close
OL,14,Ffriend, who's in a police force. He
OL,15,Fsaid at the time: 'We don't take it
OL,16,Fseriously.' It was shocking to hear
OL,17,Fthat."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
