OL,3,CDriving instructor 'still trying to
OL,4,Cfunction' after ex-pupil stalked him
OL,6,FBob's stalker appeared in court twice,
OL,7,Freceiving suspended prison sentences
OL,8,Fon both occasions - alongside an
OL,9,Findefinite restraining order.
OL,11,FThe boss of one of the watchdogs
OL,12,Finvolved in the report, the
OL,13,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,14,F(IOPC), made clear stalking victims
OL,15,Fneed to have "confidence to come
OL,16,Fforward, knowing they will be listened
OL,17,Fto and supported."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
