OL,6,FIOPC Director General Rachel Watson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Sadly, we also saw too many
OL,8,Fcases where police failed to recognise
OL,9,Fstalking or take the necessary steps
OL,10,Fto protect victims ` and policing must
OL,11,Fact now to improve this."
OL,13,FToo often the probe uncovered
OL,14,F"examples of the police not taking
OL,15,Fstalking seriously enough" and the
OL,16,Fwatchdogs found it "especially
OL,17,Fconcerning" that, in some cases,
OL,18,Fpolice "had not identified risk of
OL,19,Fserious harm or homicide to a victim."
