OL,6,FThe report did find some good practice
OL,7,Fbut made a string of recommendations
OL,8,Ffor improvement.
OL,10,FFor Bob, the report underlines how the
OL,11,Fdamage caused by stalking needs to be
OL,12,Fbetter understood.
OL,14,F"The first thing that that should be
OL,15,Fconsidered is the sheer impact," he
OL,16,Fsaid. "If it's left - worst case
OL,17,Fscenario - it's going to cost a life
OL,18,Fand, at the very least, it's going to
OL,19,Fscar you.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
