OL,3,CDriving instructor 'still trying to
OL,4,Cfunction' after ex-pupil stalked him
OL,6,F"It's got to be education. We've got
OL,7,Fto learn by all of these cases. I'm
OL,8,Fstill trying to function. I'm still
OL,9,Ftrying to go about my daily business.
OL,11,F"But I'm always on my guard. This was
OL,12,Fyears ago now and I'm always on my
OL,13,Fguard. It never goes away.
OL,15,F"Too many people are left with these
OL,16,Fmental scars - looking over your
OL,17,Fshoulder constantly.
OL,19,F"But if it's nipped in the bud before
OL,20,Fit gets this bad, then that scar is
OL,21,Fgoing to be smaller."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
