OL,3,CDriving instructor 'still trying to
OL,4,Cfunction' after ex-pupil stalked him
OL,6,FResponding to today's report, Deputy
OL,7,FChief Constable Paul Mills, from the
OL,8,FNational Police Chiefs' Council,
OL,9,Fpledged to "improve and standardise
OL,10,Fthe service victims receive."
OL,12,FHe added: "We remain committed to
OL,13,Fdoing everything possible to improve
OL,14,Fthe policing response for victims of
OL,15,Fstalking."
OL,17,FWhile the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,18,Fsaid it would continue to work with
OL,19,Fpolice to bring "robust" cases to
OL,20,Fcourt.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
