OL,6,FSafeguarding minister Jess Phillips
OL,7,Fsaid the Government would "respond
OL,8,Ffully" to the report in due course,
OL,9,Fadding of its recommendations:"We are
OL,10,Falready actively considering these,
OL,11,Flooking at how we can work with the
OL,12,Fpolice to overhaul how we respond to
OL,13,Fthis crime and put more perpetrators
OL,14,Fbehind bars."
